- @title = 'Call me!'

If you lost a pet, the 
%b Call me!
feature is the easiest one to use. Here is how it works.

%p

Enter your phone number in the box below. You will receive a call to confirm. 
For the next week, if a pet is found in your zip code, a call will be made to you - telling you the pet details. 
If your pet is described, you can send a message to the person who found it. All anonymously.

%p
 
That is it! Good luck! Please recommend this service to anyone who has lost a pet. They'll love you for it!

%fieldset
  %legend
    Call me!
    - fieldset_form_for @callme do |f|
      = f.error_messages
      = f.text_field :phone
      = f.text_field :zip
      = f.submit "Call me!"

